{"tid":1296373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔應該再戴口罩","createTime":"2019-07-08T10:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:01:12.000Z","uid":232378,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"272984c1a4ae6459a6ce63db1000e0fac3c399dc","tid":1296373,"uid":232378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"口罩易俾惡犬扯甩<br />\n上半面見到曬 啲犬又鍾意認耳仔<br />\n飲水都要冒住俾人影嘅風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以！<br />\n我建議大家使用「臉基尼」取代口罩！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AmGOPTo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmGOPTo.png&h=23608712&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4VDsE4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4VDsE4.png&h=f5c34037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個戴左個樣都一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方便飲水之餘又防曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n惡犬要扯落黎都要多啲時間 可以趁機大嗌吸引多啲巴絲幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f387bf537a1af042fd7bb959b9f008c07986a55","tid":1296373,"uid":232378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7ba6594943a18d7c2ea921e2b501bdd6dcfe3e","tid":1296373,"uid":51712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:10:10.000Z","msg":"焗撚到抽筋"},{"pid":"17178540980e5188b671c4fa0cfa11d092c07b84","tid":1296373,"uid":232378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c7ba6594943a18d7c2ea921e2b501bdd6dcfe3e","tid":1296373,"uid":51712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:10:10.000Z","msg":"焗撚到抽筋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"難認好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}